{"tid":1625101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］係咪需要停止再宣揚香港獨立？！","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:24:04.000Z","uid":219007,"like":16,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"872329f90c985bc8a280a6e351ff7f639361ceed","tid":1625101,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"我要懺悔先，我之前都覺得獨立係將來民運既主題，但係今次運動中可能需要作出策略性調整！<br />\n<br />\n香港人一個保守嘅社會，單靠自己力量根門蠃唔到，一定要靠美帝外力。我明白大家好想當家作主香港獨立，但美帝係會因為利益而反對港獨。因為作為世界三大金融中心之一既香港政體一有翻天覆地既巨變，美帝利益一定受損！加上香港獨立後美帝必定失去制衡中共既大棋子，基於呢啲理由佢一定反對香港獨立。 若大家繼續喺呢一刻宣揚香港獨立，我地隨時失去呢位盟友，運動一定失敗，之前手足既血汗就浪費！<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為港獨呢個議題應該暫時停止，要去返桿衛一國兩制，除非能夠有能力喚醒港人不再保守，真正放手一搏以死相拼先能夠有機會獨立，否則真係靠返美帝。"},{"pid":"26fdb39dcaa3e06c897447e31d12c1ae1a756aec","tid":1625101,"uid":257293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"其實裝修有好多種<br />\n點解唔裝修成連儂牆？<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論同國際支持<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72%26oe%3D5E364A79&h=7003ea3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修 + 文宣 可以同時做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee101180650c2fd3cd223b578b6a6fe1dfab5704","tid":1625101,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"昨日之事可見，任何建築於空談之上嘅政府都唔會有外國支持。因此，我有幾點建議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624597</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f200efa921252ce374c6014b409ecf1a7f0e4279","tid":1625101,"uid":313054,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"割啦，割獨立啦屌你地老母個死臭西，十鳩幾年都唔化，繼續拋個波畀下一代啦，繼續做中國大陸人啦，繼續叫啲人畀人輪姦啦。<br />\n<br />\n中國一早已經畀緊自治你，你到底抗咩爭呢？下？覺唔覺得自己鳩呢？2019啦，仲信中國會有真自治，你去食屎啦！<br />\n<br />\n全部土生土長，走在最前緣，而家畀你話係間諜哈哈哈。你要拎國際支持你獨立，唔係跟國際班利益撚嘅輿論走啊，唉，醒啲啦！"},{"pid":"c5aadae591498097d285c1d5ee1f3f14f043456f","tid":1625101,"uid":128594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"終於識醒 都算好事"},{"pid":"84ee18d4a8855cb0c1ec06aeb400e35a6343f1b9","tid":1625101,"uid":235374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"first rule of 港獨 is not to talk about 港獨"},{"pid":"d5638e5fde96c73d2bfc4fb4e86b83218cd94f87","tid":1625101,"uid":36086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"多謝你講公道說話"},{"pid":"28555005519aa6951e82f4bdce1f8b34698b009c","tid":1625101,"uid":269363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d98389d057e5e71037639bbd0d168c9793ac142e","tid":1625101,"uid":263213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84ee18d4a8855cb0c1ec06aeb400e35a6343f1b9","tid":1625101,"uid":235374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"first rule of 港獨 is not to talk about 港獨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:05:26.000Z","msg":"港獨唔洗講出黎比人聽<br />\n靜靜地贏唔得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"43c670146db209879de3b2c37d2756d88e366f4f","tid":1625101,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84ee18d4a8855cb0c1ec06aeb400e35a6343f1b9","tid":1625101,"uid":235374,"like":3,